{"id":4642,"date":"2019-02-07T19:32:26","date_gmt":"2019-02-08T00:32:26","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/deux-enseignants-du-departement-de-musique-recompenses-au-22e-gala-des-prix-opus-du-conseil-quebecois-de-la-musique\/"},"modified":"2023-06-14T13:19:51","modified_gmt":"2023-06-14T17:19:51","slug":"deux-enseignants-du-departement-de-musique-recompenses-au-22e-gala-des-prix-opus-du-conseil-quebecois-de-la-musique","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/deux-enseignants-du-departement-de-musique-recompenses-au-22e-gala-des-prix-opus-du-conseil-quebecois-de-la-musique\/","title":{"rendered":"Deux enseignants du d\u00e9partement de musique r\u00e9compens\u00e9s au 22e gala des prix Opus du Conseil qu\u00e9b\u00e9cois de la musique"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Le\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.cqm.qc.ca\/36\/Les_prix_OPUS.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gala des prix Opus du Conseil qu\u00e9b\u00e9cois de la musique<\/a> r\u00e9compense, \u00e0 chaque ann\u00e9e, des musiciens de concert d&rsquo;ici, en soulignant leur excellence et leur diversit\u00e9.<\/p>\n<p>L&rsquo;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.cqm.qc.ca\/49\/Gala_des_prix_Opus_22.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\u00e9dition 2017-2018<\/a> s&rsquo;est tenue le 3 f\u00e9vrier dernier. Au cours de celle-ci, le prix hommage a \u00e9t\u00e9 d\u00e9cern\u00e9 \u00e0 Gilbert Patenaude, longtemps directeur musical des Petits chanteurs du Mont-Royal et chef de ch\u0153ur au d\u00e9partement de musique du C\u00e9gep. \u00c9galement, Luc Beaus\u00e9jour et l\u2019ensemble <em>Clavecin en concert<\/em>\u00a0ont, quant \u00e0 eux, remport\u00e9 le prix \u00ab Concert de l\u2019ann\u00e9e, musiques m\u00e9di\u00e9vales, de la Renaissance, baroque\u00bb.<\/p>\n<p>Chaleureuses f\u00e9licitations \u00e0 tous deux\u2009!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Prix hommage de la 22<sup>e<\/sup> \u00e9dition des prix Opus \u00e0 Gilbert Patenaude, chef de ch\u0153ur du d\u00e9partement de musique, compositeur et p\u00e9dagogue accompli afin de souligner son apport important au milieu musical qu\u00e9b\u00e9cois.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4643,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[15],"sujet-actualite":[196],"etiquette-interne":[2301,2303],"class_list":["post-4642","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-nouvelle","sujet-actualite-honneurs","etiquette-interne-honneurs","etiquette-interne-musique"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-05 21:43:54","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"category"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4642","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4642"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4642\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4925,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4642\/revisions\/4925"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4643"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4642"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4642"},{"taxonomy":"sujet-actualite","embe